node.text:
Can I be honest with you? As a grown man, I do everything I can to give back to my parents! I’m not saying you have to agree with everything your parents say, but I am saying that they do the best they can for you - and we have to respect that!

On this episode of free summer school, the squad and I chop it up about the relationship you have with your parents. This is an important topic, so don’t miss it! Remember, small steps, great distances. Now you know… Let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Relationship With Parents | Summer School Series

Listen to me very closely: the information in this episode will change your life if you apply it! Are you hearing me? We’re talking about goal setting, and I promise you it’s one of the more important secrets to success. 

Come get you some of this knowledge on today’s episode of free summer school - and I’ll see you there! 

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
Look, y’all - I know from experience that fear can be a strong emotion… but it ain’t stronger than you! In this episode of free summer school: Knowledge Is The New Money, my friends and I will be walking you through how to overcome your fears.

I’m not saying it will be easy, but I am saying you can, you will, and you must overcome! So - tune in to this episode of summer school, and remember: small steps, great distances… now you know, let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Dealing with Fear | Summer School Series

node.text:
Can I keep it 100 with you? Just START. You heard me, just start! Start where you are, use what you have, and do what you can. I promise you; my life changed when I decided to stop waiting for other people to tell me what to do.

On this episode of free summer school, my friends and I are chopping it up about what becoming a self-starter looks like - and I need you locked in for this one! Remember… small steps, great distances. Now you know, let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
Look y’all, believe me when I say: the things you tell yourself matter! Stop listening to what other people say about you, and start saying amazing things about yourself!

I’m talking about SELF-affirmation, and it’s our topic for this episode of free summer school. Remember, knowledge is the new money, come get you some!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
It’s ya boy, ET! For real, this episode of free summer school is something special. Listen to me very closely: I need you to get as much of this knowledge as possible!! In this episode, my friends & I chop it up about the importance of family.

We’re talking about those people who care about us the most, y’all! Lots of things are essential in this world, but few are more important than family. Remember small steps, great distances. Now you know… let’s go! 

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Importance of Family | Summer School Series

node.text:
Look, y’all - this is a heavy topic, but it’s super important. We all deal with loss during our lives, but learning how to cope with it makes all the difference. I’ve lost five aunts to cancer, so I promise you I know what loss feels like… but I’m still standing strong! 

In this episode of free summer school, my friends and I will tell you about our experiences coping with death. If we could get through it, you can too! This one is important, so focus up, take some notes, and I’ll see you there.

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Coping with Death | Summer School Series

node.text:
Listen to me very closely: forgiveness isn’t for “them;” it’s for you. That’s right; forgiveness is actually for YOU! I didn’t blow up until I learned how to forgive others… and now, my friends and I want to teach you everything we know about forgiveness!

Make sure you’re locked in for this episode of free summer school: Knowledge is The New Money! Get you some of this knowledge so you can make the rest of your life the best of your life.

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
I’m SUPER excited about this episode of free summer school because I get to talk about superpowers. Yup, you heard me - superpowers! We all have them, and I want to help you use your powers for good! 

My friends & I will be chopping it up about introverts and extroverts and how both have their own superpowers. This episode is going to be SUPER special - and I’ll see you there!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
Can I be honest with you? As a grown man, I do everything I can to give back to my parents! I’m not saying you have to agree with everything your parents say, but I am saying that they do the best they can for you - and we have to respect that!

On this episode of free summer school, the squad and I chop it up about the relationship you have with your parents. This is an important topic, so don’t miss it! Remember, small steps, great distances. Now you know… Let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
What up! What up! What up!

Public...Service...Announcement!(Tobe/Tobe)

Calling all Video Editors!

Listen, if you can edit like nobody’s business, we need to get at you! 

If you got it like that when it comes to making video content pop, we need to get at you!

ETA is looking to contract with the baddest of the bad, the hypest, most excellent video editors around and, if you can make that video thang do what it do, we need to get at you! 

Shoot your resume and a sample of your best work to info@etinspires.com, and if what you send wows the Bajan Sensation, we’ll start the conversation!

node.text:
Look, y’all - I know from experience that fear can be a strong emotion… but it ain’t stronger than you! In this episode of free summer school: Knowledge Is The New Money, my friends and I will be walking you through how to overcome your fears.

I’m not saying it will be easy, but I am saying you can, you will, and you must overcome! So - tune in to this episode of summer school, and remember: small steps, great distances… now you know, let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾
